.page-header
  %h2 Image requests

.row
  .span4
    %h4 Basic Request

    %p Request a user's picture using their OSU name.#:

    %p
      %code #{root_url}butsko.7

  .span4
    %h4 Width

    %p
      You can request image widths from 50 to 400 pixels in 50 pixel increments by sending a
      %code width
      parameter.

    %p
      %code #{root_url}butsko.7?width=200

  .span4
    %h4 Aspect

    %p
      By default, opics are square. Pictures are also available in a 4:3 potrait aspect ratio. These can be requested by setting the 
      %code aspect
      parameter to p.

    %p
      %code #{root_url}butsko.7?aspect=p

    %p
      This works in combination with the width parameter:

    %p
      %code #{root_url}butsko.7?aspect=p&width=350